This file contains the XINS 1.3.0-alpha4 release notes.

Contents:
- Introduction
- Prerequisites
- Compatibility
- Bugs


*** INTRODUCTION ***

This is an unstable release. New features have not been tested extensively and
they may undergo major changes.

This release should be compatible with previous stable releases.


*** PREREQUISITES ***

The following are prerequisites for using the XINS framework:
- Apache Ant 1.6.2 or higher (1.6.5 recommended)
- Java SDK 1.3.1 or higher (1.4.2 recommended)


*** COMPATIBILITY ***

This release has been tested successfully in combination with Apache Ant
versions 1.6.2 to 1.6.5. See: http://ant.apache.org/
To download it, visit: http://ant.apache.org/bindownload.cgi

The 'xins' shell script in this release has been tested with bash 2.0x on
Linux 2.4/x86, Linux 2.6/x86, Mac OS/X, Solaris 8 and Cygwin 1.5.12 (on
Windows 2000).

The 'xins.bat' batch file has been tested with various Windows versions,
including Windows ME, 2000 and XP.


*** BUGS ***

To get an overview of all XINS-related bugs, or to submit a new one, visit:
http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=71598&atid=531814

